Class Message

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.timmyrs.suprdiscordbot.structures.Structure
      • de.timmyrs.suprdiscordbot.structures.Message

  • public class Message
extends Structure
    Message Structure. You can retrieve an array of message structures using Channel.getMessages(int) and a single message structure using Channel.sendMessage(String).
    Author:
    timmyRS
